Rating: 4
I've probably made this a dozen time since the recipe came out in '07. It's definately a staple during the summer months. I use the frozen clams that they sell at Costco which are very tasty even on their own. I've used fresh and frozen corn and don't really notice a difference between the two. I also a some red pepper flakes to kick it up a notch.

