Rating: 4
This was the first time I had a recipe turn out like the picture. This was delicious and for little effort and ingredients. I halved the recipe for two but kept the clams to a whole pound. I let the potatoes simmer a bit longer before adding the clams as well as tossed in a fresh bay leaf just because. I also had roasted corn from earlier in the week, but I don't think it made a huge difference. Elegant enough to serve to company. Looking forward to the next time I make it again.

