This was terrific. Although it's category is "quick" wouldn't buy into that. Cutting the corn, washing and chopping scallions and peeling and cubing potatoes, unless one has staff becomes quite time consuming. End result worth the effort. I did however find it needs some heat when served. So a blob of favorite hot sauce won't hurt.

